node.text:
Icon, pioneer, Motorcycle Hall of Fame shero, Bessie Stringfield has inspired young African-American women and motorcyclists every where.

Jay take a ride with members from the "Bessie Stringfield All-Female ride" on a '36 #Harley #Knucklehead - making him the oldest guy on the oldest bike. 😂

node.title: J-kool and the Bessie Stringfield All-Female ride
